Package com.inrupt.client.openid

Class OpenIdConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inrupt.client.openid.OpenIdConfig
  • public class OpenIdConfig
extends Object
    A class for configuring an Open ID session.

    This includes verification rules for OpenID Connect ID Tokens.
